  "description": "A large, orange grabber bucket is suspended in mid-air, actively dumping a load of dark, granular material \u2013 likely coal or a similar industrial substance \u2013 onto a gray surface below. The background is dominated by a stack of colorful shipping containers, prominently displaying the logos 'CMA CGM' and 'MAERSK'. The containers are varying shades of blue, red, and yellow, creating a vibrant contrast with the dark material being unloaded. Water sprays around the bucket, indicating a wet environment, possibly a dock or port. The scene suggests industrial activity related to cargo handling and transportation.",
